These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, metal
1. the fan of reggae is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the fan of metal and the person drinking milk##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | milk | fanta | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | jazz    | metal   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, puzzles
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, police-officer, scientist
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the scientist is between the dancer and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | board-games    | puzzles        | reading |
| Job     | police-officer | scientist | dancer         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, fanta
3 different pets are kept: pony, frog, goat
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking fanta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea     | fanta |
| Pet        | frog  | goat | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, jazz, house
3 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, pony
1. the fan of trance is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the fan of house is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the lizard##2
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | house     | trance |
| Pet           | ferret | pony | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, magic-tricks
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rat
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | drawing | magic-tricks     | video-games |
| Pet     | rat    | ferret | frog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, russian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, cricket, cycling
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the japanese and the brazilian##2
2. the brazilian is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the russian is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | russian   | japanese        |
| Sport         | cricket | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, strawberry, corn
There are 3 different nationalities: french, russian, australian
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the french is between the person eating corn and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | strawberry  | potato  | corn |
| Nationality   | russian | french | australian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, family, adventure
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, indian, american
1. the person watching family movies is the american##1
2. the indian is between the person watching family movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | animation  | family  |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian | american |

