.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, handball, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, scooter, motorbike
1. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person driving the car is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | cricket | baseball | handball  |
| Transport   | motorbike    | car        | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
