.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, pineapple, tomato
1. the person eating tomato is between the person drinking water and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | water | soy-milk      | mirinda      |
| Food       | pineapple  | tomato | kiwi |

