2. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is surfing##2
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | metal   | techno   |
| Sport         | surfing | tennis | handball |

