.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, german, argentine
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding, badminton
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the german and the argentine##2
2. the german is on the far left##1
3. the german is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | german | canadian   | argentine   |
| Sport         | badminton  | biathlon | skateboarding |

