The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, surfing, water-polo
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | crime | martial-arts |
| Sport         | skiing | water-polo | surfing      |

