.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, fantasy, action
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, ambient, gospel
1. the person watching action movies is between the fan of dubstep and the person watching thriller movies##2
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | action | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | gospel | dubstep   |

