.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, rock
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of pop##2
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | hot-chocolate   | milk |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | dubstep | pop   |

 